rs to San Francisco. Hotel is on border of not so desirable areas of town. ', 'true', 'Fri Jul 15 00:00:00 PDT 2016', 'anonymous'), ('3192', '8737', '57865cc09684e30b4ac7772b', '5', '', 'Staff is great best experience , great breakfast , room clean ,\r\nlocation the best ', 'true', 'Wed Jul 13 00:00:00 PDT 2016', 'anonymous'), ('3193', '8737', '578657a6e250ac1512d4f425', '5', 'Nice hotel close to Union Square', 'The San Francisco Marriott Marquis is a wonderful, convenient hotel near Union Square.  The staff were competent and friendly, and the concierge very helpful. Accommodations were very nice.', 'true', 'Wed Jul 13 00:00:00 PDT 2016', 'anonymous');
